				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			
		<div class="ot-accordions">
						<div class="acc-item">
				<span class="acc-toggle">What is a Domain? <i class="down flaticon-download-arrow"></i><i class="up flaticon-up-arrow"></i></span>
				<div class="acc-content">
					<p>A domain name is a system for assigning ‚Äòaddresses‚Äô to internet web servers. It is somewhat like a sign-post directing traffic to the individual space where your website is digitally located on a hosting server.</p>				</div>
			</div>
						<div class="acc-item">
				<span class="acc-toggle">Can I purchase my own Domain? <i class="down flaticon-download-arrow"></i><i class="up flaticon-up-arrow"></i></span>
				<div class="acc-content">
					<p>Yes, a Domain needs to be purchased and its registration has to be¬† renewed regularly to ensure that you remain its owner.¬†<br />To purchase a Domain, see our recommended registrar here.</p>				</div>
			</div>
						<div class="acc-item">
				<span class="acc-toggle">What is Website hosting? <i class="down flaticon-download-arrow"></i><i class="up flaticon-up-arrow"></i></span>
