					<p>Website hosting is required in order to get your website online. It is the space that you ‚Äòrent‚Äô which houses your web files and allows users to access your site and the information contained in it.<br />To host your website, please click here.</p>				</div>
			</div>
						<div class="acc-item">
				<span class="acc-toggle">Are there any other on-going costs to keep my Website published? <i class="down flaticon-download-arrow"></i><i class="up flaticon-up-arrow"></i></span>
				<div class="acc-content">
					<p>Yes, to keep your website published you will need to ensure that it remains hosted and that your domain is also valid. Also, it is necessary to have all the associated tools and addons updated.</p><p>Note that both, the website hosting and domain registration are interdependent.</p>				</div>
			</div>
						<div class="acc-item">
				<span class="acc-toggle">Do you redesign existing Websites? <i class="down flaticon-download-arrow"></i><i class="up flaticon-up-arrow"></i></span>
